name: NewSoftwares Temporary File
summary: A ### file is a temporary file created by a NewSoftwares application, such as USB Block. It typically appears in the Users/​UserName/​AppData/​Roaming/​.# folder. ### files may be detected as malware. You can permanently delete ### files only after uninstalling the NewSoftwares application that is creating the files.

open.note: Open with an associated app listed below.
